headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Stryker (SYK) After Multi Year Share Price Strength
summary: If you are wondering whether Stryker’s current share price still offers value, or if most of the opportunity is already reflected in the market, you are not alone. With the stock last closing at US$387.46 and returns of 1.9% over 7 days, 8.3% over 30 days, 11.3% year to date, 1.3% over 1 year, 46.9% over 3 years, and 70.0% over 5 years, many investors are asking what they are really paying for at today’s level.
